Package: agevarycoef
Title: Age-Varying Coefficient Models for Predicting Cognition from Neuroimaging Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ben", "Griffin", , "ben.griffin@keble.ox.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0000-7310-6074"))
Description: Implements age-varying coefficient models to predict cognitive traits using structural IDPs from the UK Biobank. Provides tools for data preparation, cross-validation, and prediction, with methods for handling missing data and age-dependent relationships between brain structure and cognition.
